snippet.title: FIVE: Champions Of Canaan Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The next step in the FIVE Saga starts today and follows the Champions of Canaan, descendants of the mighty men of FIVE: Guardians of David.

Battle for honor and glory in the bloodthirsty arenas of the ancient lands of Canaan and pit your strength and skill against the fiercest of enemies. Earn the trust of the enemy commander to prevent war from overtaking the region once more!

Join our community on Steam, Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram!

Steam: http://bit.ly/KChamp | http://bit.ly/KGuard
https://www.facebook.com/KingdomGamesATX/
https://twitter.com/KingdomGamesATX/
https://instagram.com/KingdomGamesATX/
